The agent should respect the following development workflow.

- Check out a new feature branch
- Commit changes to feature branch
- Open a PR to merge feature branch into develop branch, so tests/CI/CD can run
- PRs should only be merged into develop branch if all tests pass
- to promote develop to staging, a PR needs to be opened and all CI/CD tests need to pass before merging
- to promote staging to main, a PR needs to be opened and all CI/CD tests need to pass before merging